{"type":"message","id":"4b0a79b5","parentId":"28330115","timestamp":"2026-04-02T16:00:39.547Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ **skill 创建完成！**\n\n我已经把 ossutil 上传封装为一个技能 `ossutil-upload`，存放在 `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/skills/ossutil-upload/`：\n\n```\nskills/ossutil-upload/\n├── SKILL.md              # 技能说明文档\n└── scripts/\n    └── upload.js         # 上传脚本（可执行）\n```\n\n## 使用方法\n\n```bash\n./scripts/upload.js <local-file> <bucket> [object-name]\n```\n\n**参数说明：**\n- `local-file` - 本地文件路径（必填）\n- `bucket` - OSS 存储桶名称（必填，不需要加 `oss://` 前缀）  \n- `object-name` - OSS 对象名称（可选，默认使用本地文件名）\n\n**示例：**\n```bash\n# 上传图片到 whisper-transcribe bucket\n./scripts/upload.js /Users/liuchenglong/Downloads/photo.jpg whisper-transcribe\n\n# 上传并重命名\n./scripts/upload.js ./local.jpg whisper-transcribe remote/photo.jpg\n```\n\n技能已经在技能列表中了，以后需要上传文件到 OSS 时可以直接使用。刚才测试上传 `test-20260315001852.jpg` 也成功了 🎉"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":5577,"output":298,"cacheRead":18232,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24107,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775145633910,"responseId":"021775145634062336c0ccc8833e375a271994f02c20b098a7ee7"}}
