{"type":"message","id":"fd82371d","parentId":"ec0bbae1","timestamp":"2026-04-02T16:08:37.588Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_c9lbfwv7jabsh2hjfpi3b58k","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Whisper Transcribe + OSS Upload Agent\n\n功能:\n  1. 使用 OpenAI Whisper 转录音视频文件\n  2. 将转录结果上传到阿里云 OSS\n  3. 返回可下载的 OSS 链接\n\n用法:\n  node transcribe-and-upload.js <input-file> <bucket> [options]\n\n参数:\n  input-file    输入音视频文件路径 (必需)\n  bucket        OSS 存储桶名称 (必需)\n\n选项:\n  --language <lang>    语言代码，默认 zh (中文)\n  --model <model>      Whisper 模型大小，默认 medium (tiny|base|small|medium|large)\n  --format <format>    输出格式，默认 all (txt|vtt|srt|json|tsv|all)\n  --output-dir <dir>   本地输出目录，默认 ./whisper-output\n\n示例:\n  # 转录中文音频，上传到 whisper-transcribe bucket\n  node transcribe-and-upload.js ~/Downloads/audio.mp3 whisper-transcribe\n\n  # 使用 large 模型转录英文\n  node transcribe-and-upload.js ~/video.mp4 my-bucket --language en --model large\n\n(Command exited with code 1)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":1,"durationMs":484,"aggregated":"Whisper Transcribe + OSS Upload Agent\n\n功能:\n  1. 使用 OpenAI Whisper 转录音视频文件\n  2. 将转录结果上传到阿里云 OSS\n  3. 返回可下载的 OSS 链接\n\n用法:\n  node transcribe-and-upload.js <input-file> <bucket> [options]\n\n参数:\n  input-file    输入音视频文件路径 (必需)\n  bucket        OSS 存储桶名称 (必需)\n\n选项:\n  --language <lang>    语言代码，默认 zh (中文)\n  --model <model>      Whisper 模型大小，默认 medium (tiny|base|small|medium|large)\n  --format <format>    输出格式，默认 all (txt|vtt|srt|json|tsv|all)\n  --output-dir <dir>   本地输出目录，默认 ./whisper-output\n\n示例:\n  # 转录中文音频，上传到 whisper-transcribe bucket\n  node transcribe-and-upload.js ~/Downloads/audio.mp3 whisper-transcribe\n\n  # 使用 large 模型转录英文\n  node transcribe-and-upload.js ~/video.mp4 my-bucket --language en --model large\n\n(Command exited with code 1)","cwd":"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775146117585}}
