{"type":"message","id":"63b60523","parentId":"8bdbf393","timestamp":"2026-04-02T16:09:45.489Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ **Agent 创建成功！🎉\n\n我已经帮你创建了完整的 `whisper-transcribe-oss` Agent，它可以：\n\n1. ✅ 使用 OpenAI Whisper 自动转录音视频\n2. ✅ 自动把所有输出文件上传到指定 OSS bucket\n3. ✅ 返回所有文件的 OSS 下载地址\n\n## Agent 位置\n\n```\n/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/agents/whisper-transcribe-oss/\n├── transcribe-and-upload.js  (主脚本，可执行)\n└── README.md                 (详细说明)\n```\n\n## 使用方法\n\n```bash\nexport PATH=\"$HOME/.local/bin:$PATH\ncd /Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/agents/whisper-transcribe-oss\n./transcribe-and-upload.js <音视频文件> <bucket名称> [选项]\n```\n\n**默认配置（中文推荐）：\n- 语言: `zh`\n- 模型: `medium`\n- 输出所有格式\n\n## 测试结果\n\n刚才我们用 homebrew 的测试文件完成了端到端测试，**全部成功**：\n\n| 文件 | OSS 地址 | 大小 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| test.txt | `oss://whisper-transcribe/transcripts/test/test.txt` | 4B |\n| test.vtt | `oss://whisper-transcribe/transcripts/test/test.vtt` | 37B |\n| test.srt | `oss://whisper-transcribe/transcripts/test/test.srt` | 37B |\n| test.json | `oss://whisper-transcribe/transcripts/test/test.json` | 278B |\n| test.tsv | `oss://whisper-transcribe/transcripts/test/test.tsv` | 26B |\n\n如果你的 OSS bucket 开启了公共读，可以通过 HTTPS 访问：\n```\nhttps://whisper-transcribe.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/transcripts/test/test.txt\n```\n\n## 模型选择建议\n\n| 模型 | 适用场景 |\n|------|----------|\n| `tiny` | 快速测试，准确率较低 |\n| `small` | 平衡速度和准确率 |\n| `medium` | **中文推荐**，推荐日常使用 |\n| `large` | 追求最好准确率，速度较慢\n\n现在你可以直接用它了！😉"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":3855,"output":539,"cacheRead":27960,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32354,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775146178794,"responseId":"0217751461789372b482879bf9ba508fa4c5c25749ab55943fb02"}}
